Traitor
One of the slaves is a traitor who is willing to disclose the mystery of the Last Shelter. Fortunately he insists on speaking only with a guards' officer and will not speak to the privates. The traitor must be killed before he spills the beans!
#subobj  1
Finding the guards' mess
The treacherous slave awaits the officers in the privates' mess at the eastern river bank, in the southern sector of the irrigated fields.
#subobj  2
Finding the traitor
You can easily tell the treacherous slave apart from the soldiers by his clothes.
#subobj  3
Killing the traitor
The traitor must die before he talks!